name: Vessels 197: Protocol War
description:
In order to operate as efficiently as possible, the AI known as Protocol Alpha can uses 4 distinct avatars depending on what skills will be needed to achieve their current objective. Each of these avatars is a distinct personality and yet still a part of the whole.

Protocol War is purpose built for battle. The tank of the Protocols, they can withstand incredible punishment and deal devastating damage. If there is going to be a fight, War is the protocol you want on the front lines. War loves combat and destruction and doesn’t care who knows it (as long as they get to kill them after they find out).

Animation and Sound by the fantastic https://sirgulliver.art/
